From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: WebKitGTKWin Port <webkitgtkwin@local>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] WebKitGTKWin: include EventLoop in DocumentLoader

DocumentLoader uses Document::eventLoop().queueTask(), which needs the full
EventLoopTaskGroup definition. Unified source ordering can otherwise leave only
the ScriptExecutionContext forward declaration visible.
---
 Source/WebCore/loader/DocumentLoader.cpp | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/Source/WebCore/loader/DocumentLoader.cpp b/Source/WebCore/loader/DocumentLoader.cpp
index 78d505fd7794..0a0ce03a68e5 100644
--- a/Source/WebCore/loader/DocumentLoader.cpp
+++ b/Source/WebCore/loader/DocumentLoader.cpp
@@ -49,6 +49,7 @@
 #include "ElementChildIteratorInlines.h"
 #include "Event.h"
+#include "EventLoop.h"
 #include "EventNames.h"
 #include "ExtensionStyleSheets.h"
 #include "FormSubmission.h"
 #include "FrameDestructionObserverInlines.h"
